CatDescriptText: Portion of cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 23, 1962, pg. 13, reads: "Concert Artists - The above were featured artists in a concert presented by the Norris Music Club, at Stephen Foster Memorial Hall, recently... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing two-toned dress posed on stairs for concert presented by Norris Music Club, in Stephen Foster Memorial Hall
